original_title: St. Joseph’s College wins 49th limited over match against St. Peter’s College
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); St. Joseph's College, Colombo won the 49th limited over encounter against St. Peter's College, Colombo by 5 wickets at the SSC Grounds in Colombo on Sunday (30).
Chasing a target of 157, St. Joseph's College scored 158/5 in 40.2 overs.
